An unidentfied voice comes from the pilot's chair, "Commander we have 
just came out of trans-warp."

The commander responses, "Is this the planet were the signal is
coming 
from if so set use down."

Another voice is heard, "Commander, an asteroid has hit the engines
we 
have no control. We are going to crash."

Commander responses, "Everyone get ready for inpact."

The spaceshuttle now falls into Earth's atmosphere.
